posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1033 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'A NEW EDITION OF RENTAL LUXURY.', 'Hawthorne Hill beckons those who desire spacious living, a great location and luxurious amenities.', 'Exquisite finishes abound with nine-foot ceilings and crown molding accents, to optional cozy fireplaces and built-in desks.', "To make your life more enjoyable, we've included a fully equipped fitness center, resort-style pool and spa, and an elaborate clubroom.", 'Quick access to I-25 puts you within minutes of downtown and DIA is an easy drive away.', 'Features:', 'Oversized Closets, Cable Ready, Ceiling Fan, Balcony, Washer & Dryer In Unit, Air Conditioning, Refrigerator, Dishwasher, Microwave, Fireplace, Garbage Disposal, View, Garden Tub', 'Community Amenities:', 'Emergency Maintenance, On Site Patrol, Individual Leases, Swimming Pool, On Site Management, Public Transportation, Pet Park, Pet Friendly, Trail, Bike, Hike, Jog, Wireless Internet Access, Garage, Accepts Electronic Payments, Fitness Center, Extra Storage, Clubhouse, High Speed Internet Access, Playground, Hot Tub, Business Center, On Site Maintenance', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet Friendly*', 'Interested in more information?', 'Visit link below:', '<URL>', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'ZcEwOc41']
